{"tid":626822,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"［第一屆連登KOL選舉］","createTime":"2018-04-12T12:29:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-14T03:24:40.000Z","uid":181416,"like":4,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"8178bfb0468668201d55687c2774f3c4b749e5dd","tid":626822,"uid":181416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T12:29:27.000Z","msg":"連登膠人特別多 有真心膠亦有假膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n無論真心膠定假膠 總有一膠係左近<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n今日就同大家選出2017-2018年最令連登仔有反應嘅連登KOL（KOL唔一定係正皮最多 負皮最多都可以）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n歡迎各巴絲留言列出心目中嘅連登KOL 然後比大家留下正皮或負皮 到此貼去到1001嘅時候就會選出最多正皮同最多負皮嘅10位KOL<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n每個留言只可以舉出一位 要有名同簡短介紹佢做咗咩成為KOL<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好喇 事不宜遲 以下由我舉出第一個參選者！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f806569bea1e5f97b5f2374bcd672f6c42ffe7e","tid":626822,"uid":181416,"like":16,"dislike":45,"score":-29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T12:30:44.000Z","msg":"名：肥絲大隻<br />\n出位行為：左左右右、係喺系、肥絲老師比評語"},{"pid":"8bf3c32e0d134504b8c59b49bf4251eb385e7082","tid":626822,"uid":181416,"like":3,"dislike":45,"score":-42,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T12:35:08.000Z","msg":"名：夫子<br />\n出位行為：出埋垃圾iq題 乜鳩曹操貂蟬 比人串到面黃都繼續出"},{"pid":"bcbd96a9e6344352c0c7f6c1d5c3ffc884357bc3","tid":626822,"uid":91813,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T12:36:20.000Z","msg":"媽咪麵"},{"pid":"3ca91a28c8bbd29d1d3c3288170899fb221a0